ation\n├── .eslintrc.cjs                # Linting configuration\n└── TASK.md                       # Problem statement\n```\n\n### Key Source Files\n\n**1. `/workspace/src/events/bus.ts` (EventBus)**\n- Global event bus using module-level handler registry\n- Methods: `on()`, `off()`, `emit()`, `clear()`\n- Handlers are stored in a shared Map, not per-instance\n\n**2. `/workspace/src/events/types.ts` (Event Definitions)**\n- Event interfaces: OrderEvent, OrderCreatedEvent, OrderCancelledEvent, OrderRefundedEvent, PaymentChargedEvent, StockReservedEvent\n- Constants: ORDER_EVENTS with event names (order.created, order.confirmed, order.cancelled, order.refunded, order.payment.charged, order.stock.reserved, order.stock.released, order.notification.sent)\n\n**3. `/workspace/src/orders/service.ts` (OrderService)**\n- Creates orders, triggers order.created event\n- Charges payment via BillingService\n- Transitions to \"confirmed\" status\n- Cancels orders (requires \"confirmed\" status)\n- Refunds within 30-day window\n- 30-day refund window validation (uses >= instead of >)\n\n**4. `/workspace/src/orders/repository.ts` (OrderRepository)**\n- In-memory store for orders\n- CRUD operations: create, findById, update, findByCustomer, findByStatus\n- Returns copies to prevent mutations\n\n**5. `/workspace/src/inventory/service.ts` (InventoryService)**\n- Event handlers for order.created and order.cancelled\n- Reserves stock on order creation\n- Releases stock on order cancellation\n- Rollback on partial failure\n- Validates the order cancellation event's status field\n\n**6. `/workspace/src/inventory/repository.ts` (InventoryRepository)**\n- Tracks StockRecord: productId, available, reserved\n- Methods: setStock, getStock, reserve, release\n\n**7. `/workspace/src/billing/service.ts` (BillingService)**\n- Charges payments and stores PaymentRecord\n- Handles stock.reserved event\n- Issues refunds\n- Integrates with NotificationService\n- Private handleRefund method for REFUNDED event\n\n**8. `/workspace/src/billing/calculator.ts` (calculateOrderTotal)**\n- Calculates price breakdown: subtotal, discountAmount, taxAmount, total\n- Applies discount percentage before tax\n- Handles proper rounding\n\n**9. `/workspace/src/notifications/service.ts` (NotificationService)**\n- Manages notification templates\n- Methods: sendConfirmation, sendCancellation, sendRefundNotice\n- Tracks sent notifications\n\n### Package.json Scripts & Dependencies\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-debug-nightmare\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/ tests/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.4.0\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.0.0\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.56.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.0.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.0.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Test Files Summary\n\n**30 visible tests across 5 test suites:**\n\n1. **orders.test.ts** (11 tests)\n   - OrderService integration tests (create, cancel, refund, stock reservation)\n   - OrderRepository CRUD tests\n   - 30-day refund window edge cases\n\n2. **inventory.test.ts** (6 tests)\n   - Event handler registration and stock reservation\n   - Rollback on failure\n   - Concurrent order handling\n\n3. **billing.test.ts** (8 tests)\n   - calculateOrderTotal with various discount/tax combinations\n   - Payment charging and refund issuance\n   - Notification sending\n\n4. **events.test.ts** (5 tests)\n   - EventBus registration, emission, handler removal\n   - Multiple handlers for same event\n   - Clearing all handlers\n\n5. **notifications.test.ts** (4 tests)\n   - Confirmation, cancellation, and refund notifications\n   - Notification tracking\n\n### Build & Lint Configuration\n\n- **TypeScript**: ES2022 target, Node16 modules, strict mode, generates declarations and source maps\n- **ESLint**: TypeScript support, recommended rules, unused var warnings